{"tid":1987721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自衛】空手道JJ有嘢想講","createTime":"2020-04-24T16:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T05:14:23.000Z","uid":148315,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4868f44437c2aefc605d60d2eac81c0685f5193c","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"其實唔淨只係空手道<br />\n<br />\n學武術我認為最重要唔係打或者擋<br />\n而係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持安全距離</span></span><br />\n通常我哋空手道唔係開打嗰陣會同對手保持三隻手臂嘅距離<br />\n如果到兩隻半手臂就要高度戒備<br />\n如果近到兩個人伸直手係掂到對方拳頭就要出手<br />\n因為呢個距離人哋踏前就打到你，係危險範圍<br />\n你唔想出手就褪後，唔係就俾人打<br />\n<br />\n想講係咩呢<br />\n我發現好多人，唔只手足，包括一眾街坊<br />\n同人口角嗰陣烘到好埋<br />\n基本上得半隻一隻手臂嘅距離<br />\n差啲錫埋去咁滯<br />\n咁近嘅距離，如果對面先郁手，你實避唔到擋唔到，學過武都係咁話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXmX1Pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXmX1Pt.jpg&h=25ec9428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩日常同人嘈交以至同藍絲起衝突<br />\n請保持足夠遠嘅距離，至少係佢踏前一步都郁唔到你嘅距離<br />\n佢烘埋嚟嘅，你唔想打柒佢或者兇鳩佢就褪後，永遠保持距離<br />\n一邊褪一邊叫佢嘈交唔使烘咁埋</span><br />\n學過吓功夫嘅俾警告佢唔好嘗試打我否則自衛還擊<br />\n(佢抽把刀出嚟我就即刻華麗轉身走)<br />\n冇錯不斷褪嗰勢係會頹咗<br />\n但如果你想避免惹官非或者受傷就得<br />\n人無事先光復到香港嘛<br />\n<br />\nBTW 如果落單俾人圍屌就唔同講法<br />\n走啦仲望"},{"pid":"8de2822785db325e88713dc29647eb57fabb79b5","tid":1987721,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"有用post，推"},{"pid":"3f07e5d1b1d349d79fbf7c6c0c82103cc7f71394","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25588c2f820025ea452f67019553674afeb015ed","tid":1987721,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f021b548c9e92161e4710eec8f0a16b344c7a347","tid":1987721,"uid":288486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"936f265ac0dc8a8b3e9db8a59fc09b52d7ce2ca0","tid":1987721,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66df5cba14bc4a5bea5663c2b58434c543107786","tid":1987721,"uid":294245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁都推"},{"pid":"c23815ee5096b7db4cbfa1a8cc05f482fac6a174","tid":1987721,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"平時洗唔洗osu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5643b4f26ad1fa1825022717d14d96047d7317","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"同埋順便練埋來回跑同全速跑<br />\n轉身快跑得快好世界<br />\n拎刀都斬你唔到"},{"pid":"faa6ae633dc5af2b3d95abff758dbdb988f60d18","tid":1987721,"uid":115866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfce09e5be1340f268bd2bed70e73f800a8a8259","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c23815ee5096b7db4cbfa1a8cc05f482fac6a174","tid":1987721,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"平時洗唔洗osu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"平時要<br />\n但我認為真係要打柒對面嗰陣<br />\n鄭家穎式嗌會比較兇到對面多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c4e04e2afb47d1c3b43611ced8017b41985381","tid":1987721,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"我練開九陰白骨爪"},{"pid":"9c8f70295f00f5609dc3da8cb6fe780cc71ba04c","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"空手入白刃或者一掌打跌佢把刀就諗多咗<br />\n<a hr