"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"304f8eb80224f3bac1b178860f8c123ba47805ee","tid":1987721,"uid":187493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"如果真係走唔到要同人隻抽記得雙手護頭咁打。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWxTDNK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWxTDNK.jpg&h=cd5341f7&s={SIZE}\" />(示意圖，圖係google搵既)<br />\n<br />\n如果好似空手道個啲站姿，用手擋人腳就快但就好易俾人瘋狂打頭(打頭中幾下你都一撚定會暈低)。同埋人地出腳都係用腳擋，用手擋會痛到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n人地攞棍，越埋佢身就越唔痛。因為棍既施力點係棍頭，你越近佢手就一定唔痛仲會有機會搶佢棍啪佢關節。(叫朋友攞棍打你，你試下埋佢身。就會明我講乜)<br />\n<br />\n但點都要學下奪刀，因為如果唔好彩沒位俾你走都搏下搶唔搶到把刀。但基本上見到刀，你又沒武器就直接跑走啦。因為你用拳都打得贏刀咁你都應該係奇才嚟，可以做batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ad2edde90e279af3b2a1f04e0ef2e414cba4c9","tid":1987721,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b105785057dc939c07da225fbd974b1b19046c3b","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e527fb00422a25057b0c682b10ea8be14117bd79","tid":1987721,"uid":14188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"點睇歐錦棠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"小弟都係運動型空手道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係小薯仔<br />\n唔識評論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"真係好打既就睇MMA啦<br />\n真打既 空手道d踢技係有d用<br />\n拳好似少廢 對比泰拳黎講"},{"pid":"274b6279cb878dd2fc556a374f34f9884fa4ae0e","tid":1987721,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03ad2edde90e279af3b2a1f04e0ef2e414cba4c9","tid":1987721,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b105785057dc939c07da225fbd974b1b19046c3b","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e527fb00422a25057b0c682b10ea8be14117bd79","tid":1987721,"uid":14188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"點睇歐錦棠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"小弟都係運動型空手道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係小薯仔<br />\n唔識評論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"真係好打既就睇MMA啦<br />\n真打既 空手道d踢技係有d用<br />\n拳好似少廢 對比泰拳黎講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"MMA都只係一個比賽叫法，佢入面包咗好多唔同打法同技巧。<br />\n<br />\n真係自保就學以色列格鬥術。因為...佢會一次過教曬你點對應棍刀俾人捉著點走同關節技，類似一個懶人包咁。印象中好多學格鬥既野都只係教你拳頭對拳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係學MMA等等係街打同人好自然玩埋寢技，你都應該死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136870036d5a43f5c56ea0d2a9ae138d551a1de8","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03ad2edde90e279af3b2a1f04e0ef2e414cba4c9","tid":1987721,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b105785057dc939c07da225fbd974b1b19046c3b","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e527fb00422a25057b0c682b10ea8be14117bd79","tid":1987721,"uid":14188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"點睇歐錦棠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"小弟都係運動型空手道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係小薯仔<br />\n唔識評論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"真係好打既就睇MMA啦<br />\n真打既 空手道d踢技係有d用<br />\n拳好似少廢 對比泰拳黎講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"最大問題都唔係拳腳勁唔勁<br />\n而係真係同打天下嗰套戲個莊惠一樣<br />\n運動型冇得拳拳到肉咁打<br />\n練唔到抗打同打人個手感<br />\n所以敢分享畀大家嘅只有步法距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都諗住練吓其他嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733baeff8cf6d0a14b7b377b1ea7a13a1b4a9912","tid":1987721,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52265a3defc32ec95eece55408aa47d430ec1e00","tid":1987721,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197dea10eb99af87794cfae2bb0499b7897f288a","tid":1987721,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:25:13.000Z","msg